{"word":"Pomegranate","slug":"pomegranate","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Pomegranate</b> A fruit.<br/> Abounded in the land of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=2'>1Sa 14:2</a><br/> Brought by the spies to show the fruitfulness of the land of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=23'>Num 13:23</a><br/> Figures of the fruits of:<br/> - Embroidered on the ephod<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=28&verse=34'>Exo 28:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=39&verse=24'>Exo 39:24</a> <br/> - Carved on the pillars of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=18'>1Ki 7:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=20'>1Ki 7:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=7&verse=42'>1Ki 7:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=52&verse=23'>Jer 52:23</a> <br/> Wine made of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=22&chapter=8&verse=2'>Son 8:2</a>"}]}